author: veithen
msg: AXIOM-421: Fixed a bug in AbstractXMLStreamWriter#writeStartElement(String, String) and AbstractXMLStreamWriter#writeEmptyElement(String, String) that causes a permutation of the local name and the namespace URI. AbstractXMLStreamWriter is used by the StAX dialects for BEA's reference implementation and IBM's XLXP 1. Other StAX implementations are not affected.
A regression test for this issue will be provided by AXIOM-420.
